  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0da2\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca \u0d85\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca \u0db6\u0dc0 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc3\u0db7\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0da2\u0dd3.\u0d91\u0dbd\u0dca.\u0db4\u0dd3\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "GL Peiris, Chairman of Pohottuwa, says that he is ready to make Sajith the Prime Minister",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna President Professor GL Peiris told the BBC that he is committed to making opposition leader Sajith Premadasa the Prime Minister.",
        "When the nominations related to the selection of the successor president were called in Parliament today (July 19), the name of Dallas Alahaperuma MP was proposed by Sajith Premadasa. Professor G. L. Peiris seconded the motion.",
        "Many people are wondering whether a plan to make Dallas Alahaperuma the President and Sajith Premadasa the Prime Minister will be implemented by now.",
        "Also, a group including Sagara Kariyawasam, Secretary of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna chaired by Professor G.L. Peiris, is working for Ranil Wickramasinghe's victory.",
        "However, many MPs refrained from commenting on this matter to the media."
      ],
